%% Models as a Service - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as User/Client
    participant GW as MaaS Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Authorino as Kuadrant/Authorino<br/>Auth Engine
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MaaSAPI as maas-api<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Limitador as Limitador<br/>Rate Limiter
    participant LLMSvc as LLMInferenceService<br/>Endpoints

    Note over Client,LLMSvc: Flow 1: User Lists Available Models

    Client->>GW: GET /v1/models<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (SA or API key)
    GW->>Authorino: Auth evaluation
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Token valid (user identity)
    Authorino->>MaaSAPI: POST /v1/tiers/lookup<br/>HTTP/8080, plaintext
    MaaSAPI-->>Authorino: Tier: free|premium|enterprise
    Authorino-->>GW: Auth success + tier metadata
    GW->>MaaSAPI: GET /v1/models<br/>HTTP/8080, X-MaaS-Username, X-MaaS-Group
    MaaSAPI->>LLMSvc: GET /v1/models (per service)<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    LLMSvc-->>MaaSAPI: Model metadata
    MaaSAPI-->>GW: OpenAI-compatible models list
    GW-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,LLMSvc: Flow 2: User Issues Ephemeral Token

    Client->>GW: POST /maas-api/v1/tokens<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (user identity)
    GW->>Authorino: Auth evaluation
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Token valid
    Authorino-->>GW: Auth success
    GW->>MaaSAPI: POST /v1/tokens (prefix rewrite)<br/>HTTP/8080, X-MaaS-Username headers
    MaaSAPI->>K8sAPI: Ensure Namespace<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    MaaSAPI->>K8sAPI: Ensure ServiceAccount<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    MaaSAPI->>K8sAPI: TokenRequest (4h default)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>MaaSAPI: Ephemeral SA token
    MaaSAPI-->>GW: Token response
    GW-->>Client: Ephemeral token (JSON)

    Note over Client,LLMSvc: Flow 3: Gateway-Level Model Inference Authorization

    Client->>GW: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (SA token)
    GW->>Authorino: Auth evaluation
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Token valid
    Authorino->>MaaSAPI: POST /v1/tiers/lookup<br/>HTTP/8080
    MaaSAPI-->>Authorino: Tier level
    Authorino->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(post on llminferenceservices)
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Allowed
    Authorino-->>GW: Auth success + tier
    GW->>Limitador: Rate limit check (tier-based)
    Limitador-->>GW: Allowed
    GW->>LLMSvc: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/HTTP, Bearer Token
    LLMSvc-->>GW: Inference response
    GW-->>Client: Model response
